01. Memory leak

When each object is allocated some memory & when that memory is not de-allocated, memory leaks occurs.
This cause, poor app performance & crashes.

Detect memory leaks
Google Console, Crashes with  OutOfMemoryException, LeakCanery

Avoid Memory leaks
Mostly take care about context
Avoid inner classes, static context

